336
00:22:05,700 --> 00:22:07,230
I didn't have lunch.

337
00:22:07,870 --> 00:22:09,500
Why didn't you have lunch?

338
00:22:10,600 --> 00:22:11,930
What do you think?

339
00:22:11,970 --> 00:22:14,000
