get something to eat first.

357
00:23:12,060 --> 00:23:13,390
That sounds like a good idea.

358
00:23:14,060 --> 00:23:16,170
- I'll go and finish up then.
- Okay.

359
00:23:32,250 --> 00:23:34,670
