370
00:24:03,780 --> 00:24:06,650
Still, I don't want to eat alone.

371
00:24:06,650 --> 00:24:10,160
If you can't eat alone, there is
nothing you can do on your own.

372
00:24:10,750 --> 00:24:13,210
I'll help you, so let's practice slowly.

373
00:24:30,810 --> 00:24:33,030
Why are you sitting so far away?

374
00:24:34,650 --> 00:24:37,300
To help you think that
you're actually here alone.

375
00:25:02,840 --> 00:25:06,150
Mr. Kwon, would you like a dumpling?

376
00:25:10,580 --> 00:25:13,920
Act like you're here by yourself
