452
00:30:11,110 --> 00:30:13,160
But instead of calling me that,

453
00:30:13,820 --> 00:30:16,440
you can call me Ms... No, wait.

454
00:30:17,390 --> 00:30:18,950
Just call me Jin Sim.

455
00:30:21,160 --> 00:30:23,030
- Gosh, that's too...
- Why?

456
00:30:23,030 --> 00:30:25,960
You should treat me more comfortably
like you treat Prosecutor Yoo...

457
00:30:25,960 --> 00:30:27,430
and Prosecutor Kim.

458
00:30:27,560 --> 00:30:30,690
