00:33:07,620 --> 00:33:09,430
I'm talking about the on-the-job
training I'm doing...

504
00:33:09,430 --> 00:33:11,090
for Writer Lee's drama.

505
00:33:11,230 --> 00:33:13,650
- Yes, what about it?
- I was thinking...

506
00:33:14,700 --> 00:33:17,730
Would it be okay if I told
Mr. Kwon about it?

507
00:33:17,730 --> 00:33:19,640
Why? Why would you tell him?

508
00:33:19,870 --> 00:33:22,340
I just feel bad...

509
00:33:22,340 --> 00:33:24,410
about lying to him.

510
00:33:24,910 --> 00:33:27,700
I see him every day,
and it makes me feel guilty.

511
00:33:28,310 --> 00:33:30,080
I know Writer Lee and Mr. Yeon...

512
00:33:30,080 --> 00:33:32,190
told me to keep it a secret.

513
00:33:32,580 --> 00:33:35,820
But it's not like Mr. Kwon has a big mouth.

514
00:33:36,590 --> 00:33:40,440
So I was thinking about telling him.

515
00:33:42,830 --> 00:33:45,630
Hyuk Joon, Mr. Kwon is
a very trustworthy guy.

516
00:33:45,630 --> 00:33:47,200
If I tell him about my situation,

517
00:33:47,200 --> 00:33:48,910
I'm sure he'll understand everything.

518
00:33:48,930 --> 00:33:52,750
Yun Seo, I get that you feel uncomfortable.

519
00:33:53,000 --> 00:33:55,370
But the main point of this
project is to keep it a secret.

520
00:33:55,370 --> 00:33:58,200
Writer Lee wants all the
attention to go to her writing.

521
00:33:58,210 --> 00:34:00,040
Her first and foremost condition
was to keep it a secret...

522
00:34:00,040 --> 00:34:01,810
that you got cast for her drama...

523
00:34:01,810 --> 00:34:03,250
before an official article got released.

524
00:34:03,250 --> 00:34:04,780
We need to keep that promise.

525
00:34:05,780 --> 00:34:08,250
I'm just worried that Mr. Kwon
might get disappointed...

526
00:34:08,250 --> 00:34:09,290
if he finds out about it later on.

527
00:34:09,290 --> 00:34:12,250
So what? You won't be seeing
him again once you quit.

528
00:34:13,290 --> 00:34:16,730
Yun Seo, don't worry about
disappointing the attorney.

529
00:34:16,790 --> 00:34:18,980
Instead, worry about how disappointed...

530
00:34:19,000 --> 00:34:21,450
Mr. Yeon and I would be
if you mess up this project.

531
00:34:29,570 --> 00:34:31,710
Telling him will put me in trouble,

532
00:34:33,410 --> 00:34:35,700
but lying to him makes me feel awful.

533
00:34:36,650 --> 00:34:39,170
Will he feel betrayed
when he finds out later on?

534
00:34:40,420 --> 00:34:42,330
Because I wasn't honest?

535
00:34:53,860 --> 00:34:55,540
Yes, dried squid.

536
00:34:57,000 --> 00:34:58,600
You're late.

537
00:34:59,970 --> 00:35:02,460
Were you on a date with
the universe's goddess?

538
00:35:03,710 --> 00:35:05,580
Stop it before I kick you up there.

539
00:35:06,480 --> 00:35:08,210
How about some beer and grilled squid?

540
00:35:08,210 --> 00:35:09,270
I'm good.

541
00:35:29,400 --> 00:35:31,370
If that's what she wants,

542
00:35:32,840 --> 00:35:33,960
then I'll try.

543
00:35:36,510 --> 00:35:38,510
Ms. Jin Sim. Jin Sim?

544
00:35:40,510 --> 00:35:42,450
Jin Sim, did you get in safely?

545
00:35:42,680 --> 00:35:45,480
Jin Sim. Jin Sim. Jin Sim.

546
00:35:46,020 --> 00:35:48,920
Jin Sim, you're very pretty.

547
00:35:48,920 --> 00:35:50,180
Unbelievable.

548
00:35:53,090 --> 00:35:54,110
It looks delicious.

549
00:35:57,890 --> 00:35:59,130
Hi, Jin Sim.

550
00:35:59,260 --> 00:36:00,970
Jin Sim. Jin Sim?

551
00:36:03,100 --> 00:36:06,130
- Jin Sim.
- This is truly unbelievable.

552
00:36:08,440 --> 00:36:10,280
You were with her all day,

553
00:36:10,340 --> 00:36:12,450
yet you're here yearning for her.

554
00:36:13,180 --> 00:36:15,250
Love. It must be love.

555
00:36:15,380 --> 00:36:16,710
Why didn't you knock?

556
00:36:16,980 --> 00:36:18,790
- Can you come here?
- Why?

557
00:36:19,520 --> 00:36:22,580
Are you showing me a photo
of your gorgeous girlfriend?

558
00:36:22,590 --> 00:36:25,680
No, it's a photo of the house
you'll be moving into.

559
00:36:28,290 --> 00:36:30,510
Oh, this one looks nice.

560
00:36:30,660 --> 00:36:31,960
You can move in instantly.

561
00:36:32,200 --> 00:36:33,490
- Instantly?
- Yes.

562
00:36:34,400 --> 00:36:36,720
Don't you think that's a little harsh?

563
00:36:36,770 --> 00:36:38,000
Check the layout.

564
00:36:38,770 --> 00:36:40,640
Like this. See?

565
00:36:41,370 --> 00:36:42,900
It looks nice and all,

566
00:36:43,040 --> 00:36:45,690
but I'd rather take
my time looking for one.

567
00:36:45,910 --> 00:36:47,110
Anyway, just keep practicing.

568
00:36:53,950 --> 00:36:56,540
Jin Sim, how about we go to lunch?

569
00:37:00,360 --> 00:37:01,510
My gosh.

570
00:37:01,830 --> 00:37:04,680
- This is awful.
- Tell me about it.

571
00:37:07,120 --> 00:37:08,720
What are you two looking at?

572
00:37:08,890 --> 00:37:11,920
This video was uploaded on an
online site I frequently visit.

573
00:37:11,920 --> 00:37:13,890
Someone recorded a video...

574
00:37:13,890 --> 00:37:15,840
of middle school girls
harassing other girls.

575
00:37:15,930 --> 00:37:17,840
- Would you like to see it?
- Sure.

576
00:37:19,770 --> 00:37:21,640
Keep your promise.

577
00:37:22,100 --> 00:37:24,720
- Don't forget it next time.
- Aren't they mean?

578
00:37:25,370 --> 00:37:26,570
They are.

579
00:37:26,710 --> 00:37:28,300
What are you talking about?

580
00:37:28,640 --> 00:37:30,520
My daughter's at the police station?

581
00:37:33,180 --> 00:37:35,370
(Sangdo Police Station)

582
00:37:35,580 --> 00:37:37,490
Keep your promise.

583
00:37:37,980 --> 00:37:39,580
- Don't forget it next time.
- Hold on.

584
00:37:40,220 --> 00:37:43,360
You're saying that this girl's my daughter.

585
00:37:43,360 --> 00:37:46,800
Mom, it's not me. It really isn't!

586
00:37:48,590 --> 00:37:51,660
That's what Jin Yi claims,

587
00:37:51,660 --> 00:37:54,200
but the bullies at the school...

588
00:37:54,200 --> 00:37:56,940
who are also harassing
the girl in the video...

589
00:37:56,940 --> 00:37:58,880
as well as the victim Park Min Joo...

590
00:37:59,340 --> 00:38:00,910
all say that...

591
00:38:00,910 --> 00:38:03,640
- Jin Yi took part in it.
- It's the truth!

592
00:38:05,510 --> 00:38:08,150
She'd steal my daughter's money...

593
00:38:08,150 --> 00:38:09,780
and harass her for no reason.

594
00:38:10,780 --> 00:38:13,980
You have no idea how devastated I've been.

595
00:38:14,720 --> 00:38:17,110
The money she stole isn't
a small amount either.

596
00:38:17,690 --> 00:38:20,180
What did you spend it on?

597
00:38:20,230 --> 00:38:21,620
It wasn't me.

598
00:38:21,660 --> 00:38:23,190
- It really wasn't.
- Of course it was!

599
00:38:23,800 --> 00:38:25,470
How dare you lie to me!

600
00:38:25,630 --> 00:38:27,270
You mean little wench.

601
00:38:27,270 --> 00:38:30,240
Ma'am, I understand that you're upset,

602
00:38:30,240 --> 00:38:32,340
but nothing's been proven yet,

603
00:38:32,340 --> 00:38:33,810
so please refrain from harsh comments.

604
00:38:33,810 --> 00:38:35,010
Nothing's been proven?

605
00:38:35,010 --> 00:38:37,290
The other kids have already testified,

606
00:38:37,340 --> 00:38:39,600
and she's there in the video.

607
00:38:39,780 --> 00:38:42,120
The bully's face can't be
properly seen in the video,

608
00:38:42,120 --> 00:38:45,620
so you can't be sure that it's my daughter.

609
00:38:45,820 --> 00:38:48,500
Also, she doesn't own
a down jacket like that.

610
00:38:48,520 --> 00:38:52,120
- Still...
- I'm almost sure that it's not her,

611
00:38:52,190 --> 00:38:54,160
because that's not who she is.

612
00:38:54,460 --> 00:38:57,750
My daughter wouldn't harass and
bully her friend like that.

613
00:39:00,600 --> 00:39:02,300
Look here.

614
00:39:04,070 --> 00:39:07,330
That's what all mothers of bullies say.

615
00:39:07,370 --> 00:39:08,870
They all say that their kids are sweet.

616
00:39:10,170 --> 00:39:12,250
But your daughter isn't!

617
00:39:12,340 --> 00:39:14,250
She's mean and cruel!

618
00:39:14,340 --> 00:39:17,030
I thought I made myself clear.

619
00:39:17,650 --> 00:39:19,410
Please refrain from harsh comments.

620
00:39:20,950 --> 00:39:23,090
If you find any issues,

621
00:39:23,120 --> 00:39:24,920
please investigate according
to the procedure.

622
00:39:24,920 --> 00:39:26,040
Let's go.

623
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:29,600
I'm pressing charges.

624
00:39:29,790 --> 00:39:31,520
I'll sue you!

625
00:39:38,000 --> 00:39:40,850
Don't worry. I'll take care of this.

626
00:39:41,740 --> 00:39:44,420
Thanks for believing me.

627
00:39:44,670 --> 00:39:46,510
There's no need to thank me.

628
00:39:46,510 --> 00:39:48,340
It's a mom's job to believe her children.

629
00:39:53,320 --> 00:39:55,320
You should get going.
You'll be late for class.

630
00:39:55,950 --> 00:39:58,870
Buy a snack if you get hungry.

631
00:40:00,690 --> 00:40:03,410
All right. I'll get going then.

632
00:40:04,090 --> 00:40:05,250
Take care.

633
00:40:18,170 --> 00:40:19,300
I see.

634
00:40:20,910 --> 00:40:22,740
Don't worry, Ms. Yang.

635
00:40:22,950 --> 00:40:26,110
Why would you when all we
have are attorneys here?

636
00:40:26,620 --> 00:40:28,860
Of course. We'll talk
more in detail tomorrow.

637
00:40:29,020 --> 00:40:31,390
Don't worry too much, okay?

638
00:40:34,190 --> 00:40:36,200
Is Ms. Yang in some sort of trouble?

639
00:40:38,160 --> 00:40:42,210
Her daughter Jin Yi was
named as a school bully.

640
00:40:43,470 --> 00:40:45,410
She seems to have been framed.

641
00:40:45,840 --> 00:40:48,520
- Could you perhaps help her out?
- Of course.

642
00:40:49,140 --> 00:40:51,760
Really? That's unexpected.

643
00:40:52,780 --> 00:40:55,220
What do you mean?
Is that what you think of me?

644
00:40:55,310 --> 00:40:56,430
You're prickly,

645
00:40:56,850 --> 00:40:57,930
but also talented.

646
00:40:59,580 --> 00:41:02,820
Anyway, help her in any way you can.

647
00:41:02,820 --> 00:41:04,960
Ms. Yang only has Jin Yi, remember?

648
00:41:13,000 --> 00:41:14,460
Unbelievable.

649
00:41:15,000 --> 00:41:16,400
How dare they say that about my daughter.

650
00:41:28,040 --> 00:41:29,070
Gosh.

651
00:41:30,980 --> 00:41:33,220
Is it so hard to hang your clothes back up?

652
00:41:34,080 --> 00:41:36,570
Goodness, let me see.

653
00:41:50,300 --> 00:41:51,700
The number you have called...

654
00:41:54,540 --> 00:41:56,680
Why isn't she picking up?

655
00:41:58,340 --> 00:41:59,400
It can't be true.

656
00:41:59,640 --> 00:42:01,720
Is this how it's going to be?

657
00:42:04,080 --> 00:42:07,790
Jin Yi, I didn't do it on purpose.

658
00:42:22,900 --> 00:42:25,340
Ms. Yang, don't look so glum.

659
00:42:26,200 --> 00:42:29,940
Our top attorney has agreed
to help you, so why worry?

660
00:42:30,310 --> 00:42:33,190
He's right. There's no need to worry.

661
00:42:33,340 --> 00:42:34,630
I'm sure it'll all work out.

662
00:42:35,240 --> 00:42:38,820
From what I hear,
your daughter has been framed.

663
00:42:40,580 --> 00:42:44,120
I don't think she was.

664
00:42:49,530 --> 00:42:50,580
I guess...

665
00:42:51,790 --> 00:42:53,940
I didn't raise her right.

666
00:43:16,750 --> 00:43:18,660
She was bullying her friend.

667
00:43:21,960 --> 00:43:25,190
When I asked her where she
got her down jacket from,

668
00:43:26,430 --> 00:43:28,330
she couldn't answer me.

669
00:43:29,200 --> 00:43:30,320
I think...

670
00:43:31,670 --> 00:43:34,250
she bought it with the money
she took from the other kids.

671
00:43:39,210 --> 00:43:41,040
I always felt sorry for her...

672
00:43:42,040 --> 00:43:43,580
because I couldn't provide much,

673
00:43:45,510 --> 00:43:48,200
but I was confident I loved her
more than any other parent could.

674
00:43:51,420 --> 00:43:53,150
I'm not sure about anything else,

675
00:43:54,190 --> 00:43:57,290
but I thought I raised her into
a kind and sincere daughter.

676
00:43:59,730 --> 00:44:01,080
But how could she...

677
00:44:01,860 --> 00:44:03,460
How could she do that?

678
00:44:07,670 --> 00:44:08,920
Ms. Yang.

679
00:44:33,800 --> 00:44:35,150
What should we do?

680
00:44:35,460 --> 00:44:37,710
Ms. Yang went through so much raising her.

681
00:44:40,340 --> 00:44:43,630
Are you sure the girl in the
white down jacket is Jin Yi?

682
00:44:44,440 --> 00:44:47,230
Considering the circumstances.
Ms. Yang said so too.

683
00:44:48,240 --> 00:44:51,610
Jin Yi is consistently denying
that she didn't do it.

684
00:44:51,780 --> 00:44:53,680
And usually in these types of situations,

685
00:44:53,850 --> 00:44:55,930
the parents are the ones who
lack objectivity the most.

686
00:44:56,320 --> 00:44:57,980
Because they can't help
but react emotionally.

687
00:44:59,160 --> 00:45:01,610
For that reason, we need to
focus just on the facts.

688
00:45:02,160 --> 00:45:03,190
You're right.

689
00:45:03,190 --> 00:45:05,610
We can't confirm the
assailant's face properly.

690
00:45:05,900 --> 00:45:09,290
And the statement that Jin Yi is
the assailant may not be true.

691
00:45:09,500 --> 00:45:11,610
As long as we're on this case,

692
00:45:12,130 --> 00:45:14,750
we shouldn't make any
prejudgments whatsoever...

693
00:45:14,800 --> 00:45:15,930
that our client is guilty.

694
00:45:15,970 --> 00:45:18,940
Then like you said, I'll go listen
to Jin Yi and think about this...

695
00:45:18,940 --> 00:45:21,150
- from her perspective.
- Okay.

696
00:45:27,250 --> 00:45:29,330
Is it okay if I go with Ms. Oh?

697
00:45:31,720 --> 00:45:32,980
Sure, go ahead.

698
00:45:36,460 --> 00:45:39,860
I heard a lot about you from Ms. Yang.

699
00:45:40,660 --> 00:45:43,830
I always wanted to meet you.
It's nice to finally meet.

700
00:45:45,840 --> 00:45:47,060
It's not me.

701
00:45:47,670 --> 00:45:49,540
I really didn't do it.

702
00:45:51,940 --> 00:45:54,150
I know. We believe you.

703
00:45:57,550 --> 00:46:01,150
So can you tell us honestly?

704
00:46:03,850 --> 00:46:07,220
The victim pointed you out as the person...

705
00:46:07,220 --> 00:46:08,240
who bullied her.

706
00:46:08,420 --> 00:46:09,750
Why do you think she did that?

707
00:46:11,060 --> 00:46:13,680
Did she have a grudge on you from before?

708
00:46:13,830 --> 00:46:15,330
I didn't even know her.

709
00:46:15,330 --> 00:46:16,800
Then what about the other bullies?

710
00:46:16,800 --> 00:46:19,800
The ones who blamed you for everything.
You don't know them?

711
00:46:27,080 --> 00:46:30,170
Then can you tell me
about your down jacket?

712
00:46:30,180 --> 00:46:32,120
Your mom said she didn't
know how you got it.

713
00:46:34,550 --> 00:46:36,760
I'm sorry, but I'll leave now.

714
00:46:37,390 --> 00:46:40,720
My mom doesn't even believe me.
What more can I say?

715
00:46:44,690 --> 00:46:45,750
- Jin Yi.
- Wait.

716
00:46:47,960 --> 00:46:49,730
Isn't she the one in that video?

717
00:46:49,900 --> 00:46:51,330
She doesn't look like a bully.

718
00:46:51,330 --> 00:46:53,710
I know. What's wrong with her?

719
00:46:59,070 --> 00:47:00,130
Jin Yi.

720
00:47:02,410 --> 00:47:05,410
Why are you following me?
I have nothing more to say.

721
00:47:07,450 --> 00:47:10,040
By any chance, do you...

722
00:47:11,150 --> 00:47:13,200
like tteokbokki?

723
00:47:14,020 --> 00:47:15,080
What?

724
00:47:20,930 --> 00:47:22,120
How did it go?

725
00:47:23,000 --> 00:47:25,880
Well, Jin Yi kept refusing to talk to me.

726
00:47:27,440 --> 00:47:29,070
But it seems that Jin Yi...

727
00:47:29,070 --> 00:47:31,350
isn't a girl who would
do something like that.

728
00:47:32,210 --> 00:47:35,440
Maybe she's being threatened.

729
00:47:35,510 --> 00:47:37,720
Threatened? By whom?

730
00:47:39,320 --> 00:47:40,880
Do you mean the real assailant?

731
00:47:43,850 --> 00:47:45,620
Is that why she can't say anything...

732
00:47:46,090 --> 00:47:48,770
even when she's being framed?
Because she's afraid?

733
00:47:49,290 --> 00:47:52,430
Usually, there are two reasons
why victims don't point out...

734
00:47:52,430 --> 00:47:53,480
the assailant.

735
00:47:53,500 --> 00:47:55,330
They're either being
threatened by the assailant,

736
00:47:55,430 --> 00:47:58,250
or they want to protect the assailant.

737
00:47:59,840 --> 00:48:02,040
For Jin Yi's case, I think it's the latter.

738
00:48:06,210 --> 00:48:08,140
According to the statements
from the victim's parent,

739
00:48:08,140 --> 00:48:11,340
the victim suffered from
continuous bullying at school.

740
00:48:11,450 --> 00:48:13,850
- So to check if it was true,
- Hold on.

741
00:48:13,850 --> 00:48:17,460
I checked the footage of whenever
Jin Yi and the victim were together.

742
00:48:17,490 --> 00:48:20,990
Yes. She's the girl who fought with
Jin Yi in front of the academy.

743
00:48:22,220 --> 00:48:24,710
I thought Jin Yi was bullying her.

744
00:48:29,630 --> 00:48:30,750
Excuse me.

745
00:48:31,600 --> 00:48:32,650
Who are you?

746
00:48:33,000 --> 00:48:34,290
I'm Seo Jin Yi's mom.

747
00:48:36,640 --> 00:48:38,440
Do you have time to talk?

748
00:48:39,210 --> 00:48:41,610
The assailant, Park Seon Yeong, was...

749
00:48:41,610 --> 00:48:44,260
close friends with Jin
Yi since they were kids.

750
00:48:44,550 --> 00:48:46,050
But at a certain point,

751
00:48:46,120 --> 00:48:49,380
she started hanging out with
other bullies and started to change.

752
00:48:49,720 --> 00:48:51,660
She borrowed Jin Yi's down jacket...

753
00:48:51,820 --> 00:48:53,240
and assaulted the victim.

754
00:48:53,290 --> 00:48:55,500
That video spread across the internet,

755
00:48:55,890 --> 00:48:59,290
and the real assailant framed
the owner of the jacket, Jin Yi...

756
00:48:59,290 --> 00:49:00,480
because she was afraid of being punished.

757
00:49:00,830 --> 00:49:04,370
Then the reason Jin Yi
didn't mention this is...

758
00:49:04,430 --> 00:49:06,130
They were close friends
since they were young.

759
00:49:06,470 --> 00:49:08,100
And she still had affection for her.

760
00:49:08,370 --> 00:49:10,240
I think Jin Yi was waiting
until she confessed.

761
00:49:12,410 --> 00:49:15,670
